{[%evp 0,31,27,10,22,25,31,4,14,-42,38,42,59,27,18,17,32,29,61,49,46,22,24,32,45,45,50,62,48,-6,-2,-29,216,200] [#]} {[%tqu "En","White to move.","","","a2a4","As a rule, this can't be a bad inclusion if Black can't make use of the b4 square, since White wants to take space and stop b5 or provoke Black's ...a5, which weakens the structure overall.",10,"f2f4","is premature.",0]} 13. a4 $5 {[%csl Ga4][%cal Ga4a5,Rb7b5] As a rule, this can't be a bad inclusion if Black can't make use of the b4 square, since White wants to take space and stop b5 or provoke Black's ...a5, which weakens the structure overall.} (13. f4 $6 {is premature.} Qb6 $1 {Strong reply.} 14. Bf2 Qxb2 15. Qd2 Qa3 $15 {[%csl Ga3] Black has the a3 escape.}) 13... a5 14. f4 $14 {Now it's a good time to grab space, since:} Qb6 $2 {[%csl Ga4,Ra5] is bad with this inclusion.} 15. Bf2 Qxb2 16. Qd2 $18 {[%csl Ga1,Ga4,Rb2][%cal Rb2a3,Ge1b1] White is winning, because Black doesn't have the a3 escape square.} *

